name: "PORTAL" - RECHARGE Part II
description: "...it has taken so long, but I've arrived finally at the Great Portal. They said I had to close my eyes in order to not lose my mind. But I don't want to see the ghosts of my past anymore. Since I left, they've been haunting me in my sleep. I even lost most of the memories of you and me..."  Words, Visuals and Soundtrack by SBAB Studio
